 accuracy\nsolution for a_P and, possibly, will lead to an unambiguous determination of\nthe origin of the Pioneer anomaly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2005 21:49:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2006 21:43:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
