uous single-frequency wave (which contains infinite energy) building up\ninfinite reactive fields during the infinite duration of time from t=-infinity\nto the present time t that the single-frequency excitation has been applied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2005 16:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2006 20:34:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Apr 2006 02:07:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-28"}
